trans-unit.source: Represents a collision record resulting from a collision between forest trust records.
trans-unit.target: Representa um registro de colisão resultante de uma colisão entre os registros de relação de confiança de floresta.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collision record from the underlying Active Directory Domain Services service.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o registro de colisão do serviço do Active Directory Domain Services subjacente.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> containing the collision record resulting from a collision between forest trust records.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que contém o registro de colisão resultantes de um conflito entre os registros de relação de confiança de floresta.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" /> value for the forest trust collision.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" /> para a colisão de confiança da floresta.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" /> value indicating the collision type.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" /> valor que indica o tipo de colisão.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions" /> value for the forest trust collision.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions" /> para a colisão de confiança da floresta.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions" /> value that provides information about the collision when the <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType" /> type is <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions" /> valor que fornece informações sobre a colisão quando o <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType" /> é do tipo <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions" /> value for the forest trust collision.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions" /> para a colisão de confiança da floresta.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions" /> value that provides information about the collision when the <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType" /> type is <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions" /> valor que fornece informações sobre a colisão quando o <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType" /> é do tipo <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType" />.
